* &quot;Poems of David Martin 1938-58&quot; (1958)
* &quot;The Gift: Poems 1959-65&quot; (1966)
* &quot;The Idealist&quot; (1968)
* &quot;I Rhyme My Time : A Selection of Poems for Young People&quot; (1980)
* &quot;Foreigners&quot; (1981)
* &quot;Peppino&quot; (1983)
