* &quot;Symphonies of Sickness&quot; (1989)
* &quot;Necroticism – Descanting the Insalubrious&quot; (1991)
* &quot;Heartwork&quot; (1993)
* &quot;Swansong&quot; (1996)
* &quot;Surgical Steel&quot; (2013)
* &quot;Torn Arteries&quot; (2021)

